、兩個鉗、一支士巴拿、一個電鑽和一支撬棍；以及未獲得通訊事務管理局授予的適當許可下，管有一套無線電收發器。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，案發時有約100名示威者於灣仔一帶集結，被告與4、5人在灣仔站A1出口外逗留，見到警察後逃跑，之後被捕。<strong><span class=\"red\">裁判官杜浩成質疑控方的提控，說「這是一個奇怪決定」，案情稱被告為示威者，又說附近有非法示威，不解為何只有兩條控罪。但控方回應稱，一度考慮控告非法集結，但「現時沒有足夠證據證明被告與示威活動有關」。杜官表示不明白，認為律政司應審視整體的環境證供，考慮是否有其他更適合的控罪。</span></strong>控方承諾會再向律政司索取指示。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057d64759abe8aa80d4e52ad38b58552504cfdc4","tid":2155855,"uid":65738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EKYm7UKUUAAnIFj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEKYm7UKUUAAnIFj.jpg&h=9be75037&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb9b633d5ce4e14f542176eeebe350dd8b8fc6b5","tid":2155855,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"057d64759abe8aa80d4e52ad38b58552504cfdc4","tid":2155855,"uid":65738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EKYm7UKUUAAnIFj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEKYm7UKUUAAnIFj.jpg&h=9be75037&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"本身繼續佢負責就大鑊"},{"pid":"32dd7b146186f03ef22534d221b0b634cd5d251b","tid":2155855,"uid":65738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb9b633d5ce4e14f542176eeebe350dd8b8fc6b5","tid":2155855,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"057d64759abe8aa80d4e52ad38b58552504cfdc4","tid":2155855,"uid":65738,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:39:49.0